#
# VERCEL_PROJECT_ID=prj_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
#   - Find at: Project Settings â†’ General â†’ Project ID
#   - Or from URL: https://vercel.com/[org]/[project] â†’ Settings
#
# For Supabase in CI (same as local, but add to GitHub Secrets):
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=eyJ...
#
# Note: NEXT_PUBLIC_ vars are safe to expose (public by design).
# The anon key only has permissions defined by your RLS policies.
